title: Trinidad And Tobago Money Supply M2
description: Money Supply M2 in Trinidad And Tobago increased to 97993.20 TTD Million in August from 96977.90 TTD Million in July of 2022. Money Supply M2 in Trinidad And Tobago averaged 43240.50 TTD Million from 1991 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 99286.20 TTD Million in January of 2021 and a record low of 9021.20 TTD Million in February of 1992. This page provides - Trinidad And Tobago Money Supply M2- actual values, historical data, forecast, chart, statistics, economic calendar and news.
author: Central Bank of Trinidad and Tobago
